Reaper- (6)
- The reaper starts the game in the underworld, and has the ability to descend to the mortal plane during the day.
- If they are in the mortal plane, they can choose to ascend to the underworld during the day.
- During nights, if the reaper in the underworld, they have weak protection. If in the mortal plane, they can choose to weak attack any one person.
- Attack is night end. Counts as a visiting action. Has no cooldown for switching worlds.
- Respawns in 3 phases.
